      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a fantastic car. It\u2019s in really great shape, runs like a total dream, and has clearly been well-loved over the years. Whether you're commuting or heading out on a road trip, this beauty is ready to go! It\u2019s super reliable and looking for its next adventure. Come take it for a spin\u2014you're going to love how it handles!",
