    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This 2004 BMW M3 (E46) is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. Power is sent to the rear wheels via a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory variable M Differential Lock. The mechanical profile is strong: the VANOS system has been recently serviced, and the rear subframe has been inspected for structural integrity. Suspension remains taut with upgraded Bilstein dampers and refreshed poly-bushings, maintaining the chassis's legendary lateral grip and steering feedback. While the Carbon Black finish shows minor road wear, the drivetrain is exceptionally dialled-in, offering the precise throttle response and linear power delivery expected of a well-maintained S54.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_3",
