      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle offers a perfect balance of performance and long-term reliability. The exterior retains a deep, glossy finish, showing only minor signs of careful road use. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and smoke-free, featuring well-preserved upholstery and a full suite of functional electronics, from the crisp infotainment system to the dual-zone climate control. Mechanically, this car shines: the engine is responsive, the transmission shifts seamlessly, and it has a documented history of timely oil changes and preventative maintenance. It drives straight, brakes firmly, and is ready to provide its next owner with years of dependable service.",
      "price": 34500.0,
